skdetail:

Invocation Name: interview prep
des: Interview Prep helps you practice critical interview questions with its database of 1000 questions. The questions cover a wide range of topics, ranging from HR to aptitude to strategy. Use Interview Prep a few times a day to best prepare yourself for your next job interview. For optimal results, sit in front of a mirror while responding and also focus on your body language.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
